# blagger

## Fetch me:

    $ git clone git://eris.cobaltirc.org/blagger.git

## Config me:

    $ vim blagger.conf

## Start me:

    $ hypnotoad blagger

## Blag stuff using Markdown:

    $ ./blagger blag this-new-entry

See _examples/_ for example posts.

